'''Asesmel anezway n  Köppen''' d yiwet n telmest n [[asesmel n inezwa|usesmel n inezwa]] ibedden neɣ yebnan ɣef [[azeqziq|yizeqziqen]] d [[Taẓɣelt|tfesniwin n teẓɣelt]], asesmel-a yesnulfa-t-id umesnezway Analman-rusan [[Wladimir Peter Köppen]] deg useggas n [[1900]] ass mi i d-issegrew tagertilt n [[tamɣawt|temɣawt]] i d-iffɣen deg useggas n [[1866]], yakk d tgertilt n beṭṭu n unezwu ɣef 5 n tɣulin n [[Alphonse Pyrame de Candolle]].<ref name="peel">{{En}} M.C. Peel, B.L. Finlayson & T.A. MacMahon, "Updated world map of the Köppen-Geiger climate classification" in Hydrology and Earth System Sciences {{Numéro|11}}, {{P.|1633}}, Copernicus Publications pour [[European Geosciences Union]], Göttingen, 2007, ISSN 1027-5606, [http://www.hydrol-earth-syst-sci.net/11/1633/2007/hess-11-1633-2007.html Updated world map of the Köppen-Geiger"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171229112144/https://www.hydrol-earth-syst-sci.net/11/1633/2007/hess-11-1633-2007.html |date=29 dujamber 2017}}</ref>

Asesmel-ayi i d amulan yakk seld mi i d-t-yesrem umesnezway Analman [[Rudolf Geiger]] deg useggas n [[1961]], anda aṭas n tegmayin d tsufaɣ yezzin ɣef [[Anezwu|unezwu]] ggunint ɣef yiwet seg waṭas n telsura yeṭṭafaren anagraw-a. Dɣa tagertilt n '''Köppen-Geiger''' tezga d nettat i d amnir deg [[tusnazwayt]] d [[tasnudert|tesnudert]] d [[tasnamurt|trakalt]] s uglaz n usetrer-is i d-yettilin deg yal tikkelt.

